WHY TO JOIN TRINITY : Trinity is one of the most prestigious and interactive student organizations of our institution. What sets apart our society from others is that all the members collaborate with each other and work on different projects and this creates a wholesome experience for all. At trinity, we believe in mutual support. Whether you are a newbie or an experienced one, we guarantee that you will learn something new and add to your resume. With our thoughtfully tailored events and meetings, we provide every member a platform where new ideas are heard and acted upon. This creates a shared space for our members and propels further growth for the society and individual members
